title: GettingStarted
tags: 

Welcome to the ''TiddlyWiki Timelord'' plugin demo!
This edition showcases the features of the plugin.

* See the [[Installation]] tiddler to install the plugin in your own wiki.
* See the [[Showcase]] tiddler for a pre-populated timelord — click the ''Revisions'' tab in the tiddler info panel to view it in action.
* Try editing tiddlers or creating new ones, then return to the Revisions tab to see the captured history and diffs.
